00:19:24.300 --> 00:19:27.450
in five years, changing
school midyear and so forth.

00:19:27.450 --> 00:19:31.920
And he came into LA disconnected,
isolated, leaving a community

00:19:31.920 --> 00:19:36.720 position:56%
in the early '90s when violent crime
