00:19:49.100 --> 00:19:50.940
till I was working on
this book, all right?

00:19:50.940 --> 00:19:54.020
This is what I mean
about shame and silence.

00:19:54.020 --> 00:19:55.320
And what it turns out is

00:19:55.320 --> 00:19:56.820
like everybody had a
little piece of the story.

00:19:56.820 --> 00:19:59.190
