00:20:05.350 --> 00:20:09.170
So one of the key lessons for me in
this whole experience has just been

00:20:09.170 --> 00:20:12.510
about the importance of bringing
these stories to the surface

00:20:12.510 --> 00:20:16.330
and the importance especially
for young people ages 10 to 14,

00:20:16.330 --> 00:20:19.870
of the adults in their lives,
like break through the shame,

00:20:19.870 --> 00:20:21.360
break through the trouble,

00:20:21.360 --> 00:20:24.280
break through the competition,
break through the envy.

00:20:24.280 --> 00:20:26.920
You've got to talk to each
