00:21:36.700 --> 00:21:41.070
to the legal state, with incredibly
powerful mechanisms of sanction,

00:21:41.070 --> 00:21:43.820
itself, that counteract
the mechanisms

00:21:43.820 --> 00:21:45.350 position:56%
