over and over and over again.

00:21:52.470 --> 00:21:55.040
So the story that I am
trying to tell is really one

00:21:55.040 --> 00:21:57.260
about how we think
about young people,

00:21:57.260 --> 00:21:59.380
how we think about the
opportunities we present to them,

00:21:59.380 --> 00:22:03.410
how we protect them, how we make
the world safe for them and ensure

00:22:03.410 --> 00:22:05.550
